        <updateDate>2010-10-19T14:18:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>American Manufacturing Disaster Relief Act of 2010 - Amends the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 to prohibit the United States Agency for International Development (USAID) from procuring manufactured articles for disaster or emergency assistance in a foreign country unless the articles are manufactured in such foreign country or, under certain circumstances, in the United States or third countries.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
